        "title": "Cope with a toxic family",
        "imageURL": "https://cdn.betterme.world/meditation/playground_microed/microed_illustrations_test/card2.png",
        "header": "Microlearning",
        "description": "How to overcome negative upbringing and childhood trauma"
      },
      "preview": {
        "title": "Cope with a toxic family",
        "imageURL": "https://cdn.betterme.world/meditation/playground_microed/microed_illustrations_test/preview.png",
        "overview": "Daily interactive stories about overcoming childhood trauma and growing as a person. Read about how different people have confronted and evaluated their experiences, and find out what helped them move past them. After completing the course, you will understand how childhood experiences can affect adult life, how parents can lead a child astray and how to get back on it later. Travel along with the characters through short interactive stories to understand how to overcome childhood traumas and apply it in your life."
      },
